text: Strange Conquest is a 1946 American drama film directed by John Rawlins and written by Roy Chanslor. The film stars Jane Wyatt, Lowell Gilmore, Julie Bishop, Peter Cookson, Milburn Stone, Samuel S. Hinds and Abner Biberman. The film was released on May 10, 1946, by Universal Pictures. ==Plot== ==Cast== *Jane Wyatt as Dr. Mary Palmer *Lowell Gilmore as Dr. Paul Harris *Julie Bishop as Virginia Sommers *Peter Cookson as William Sommers *Milburn Stone as Bert Morrow *Samuel S.
